# Voice-Settings: stability=0.66 | similarity_boost=0.42 | speed=1.02
# Sample-Referenz: public/sounds/pauli/liam-voice-reference.mp3
# =============================================================================
# Schritt 1: ElevenLabs-Dashboard → Voices → "Liam" → Copy Voice ID → hier eintragen
